@startuml User Journey
!include ../PlantUML/config.cfg

title AgentCode Framework - User Journey

' === USER ACTIONS ===
|User|
start
:Type /generate-docs MyProject;

|#LightGray|Backend (System)|
:doc-coordinator receives command;
:Create docs/MyProject/ structure;

fork
  :SRS Workflow;
  :Spawn @srs-agent &;
  :requirements-agent interviews user;
  :Spawn 5 uc-diagram-agents (parallel);
  note right
    Each UC agent creates 6 diagrams:
    - use-case
    - screenflow
    - statediagram
    - sequence
    - class-backend
    - class-frontend
  end note
  :Verify all diagrams created;
  :Write SRS document;
fork again
  :SDD Workflow;
  :Spawn @sdd-agent &;
  :Spawn 6 component-agents (parallel);
  note right
    Each component agent creates 5 artifacts:
    - class-backend.puml
    - class-frontend.puml
    - sequence.puml
    - state.puml
    - db/tables/xxx_tables.sql
  end note
  :Spawn db-agent + api-agent;
  :Verify all components created;
  :Write SDD document;
end fork

:Generate index.md;
:Package all outputs;

|User|
stop

note right of |User|
  **What User Sees:**
  1. Command entered
  2. Progress indicator
  3. Final document list

  **What Happens:**
  18 agents run in parallel
  32+ files generated
  ~2 minutes total
end note

@enduml
